# prefix-block-no-indent-body

## Input

```
s {
k v
m 2
}

```

## CST

```
SOURCE_FILE@0..14
  PREFIX_BLOCK@0..14
    WORD_KEY@0..1
      WORD@0..1 "s"
    SPACE@1..2 " "
    OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{"
    NEWLINE@3..4 "\n"
    ENTRY@4..8
      WORD_KEY@4..5
        WORD@4..5 "k"
      SPACE@5..6 " "
      LINE_STRING@6..7
        STRING@6..7 "v"
      NEWLINE@7..8 "\n"
    ENTRY@8..12
      WORD_KEY@8..9
        WORD@8..9 "m"
      SPACE@9..10 " "
      INTEGER@10..11
        NUMERAL@10..11 "2"
      NEWLINE@11..12 "\n"
    CLOSE_BRACE@12..13 "}"
    NEWLINE@13..14 "\n"
```

## AST

```
SourceFile {
    shebang: none,
    items: [
        PrefixBlock {
            key: WordKey {
                word: WORD@0..1 "s",
            },
            open_brace: OPEN_BRACE@2..3 "{",
            items: [
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@4..5 "k",
                    },
                    value: LineString {
                        string: STRING@6..7 "v",
                    },
                },
                Entry {
                    key: WordKey {
                        word: WORD@8..9 "m",
                    },
                    value: Integer {
                        sign: none,
                        numeral: NUMERAL@10..11 "2",
                    },
                },
            ],
            close_brace: CLOSE_BRACE@12..13 "}",
        },
    ],
}
```

